ticle/20170308/s00001/1488982487837</a></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 射波比其他人其他部門，你就真心膠覺得佢幫你"},{"pid":"044946ca0780b8cc73b1622f1c12d0b5b834a2a6","tid":148634,"uid":19654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T17:27:21.000Z","msg":"又學john tsang搵名人拍片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9f58c6cca65982a80ee199329bbfcdf7055114b","tid":148634,"uid":9053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T17:57:14.000Z","msg":"有撚用咩<br />\n<br />\n廢老都冇票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢刻廢老一定巴不得有真普選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8978494ce62f7ae0c575a09d6eb179e32ae98e8e","tid":148634,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T23:27:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"142fc62605220b3529431c3894cf365ec029a787","tid":148634,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T00:04:42.000Z","msg":"證明女人係唔撚適合搞政治"},{"pid":"cf4c351f9649b8a48594dea1337b4e6269e1cf34","tid":148634,"uid":37666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T00:06:40.000Z","msg":"芬芬姐幫下朋友啫"},{"pid":"243b23b2aa3c0f9e0bde4b25001d988009a27578","tid":148634,"uid":76563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T00:07:54.000Z","msg":"自甘墮落 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11ede131f4d52247d18f694ecbb1381a13f1f060","tid":148634,"uid":36820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T00:11:31.000Z","msg":"ON99，擺明係利益輸送啦，名人就特事特辦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgm